v0.3.0: Expanded - macOS Glass Theme, Trash preview, dialogs, fixes

New features:
- macOS Glass Theme with backdrop-filter blur
- Trash panel with note preview, styled restore/delete buttons
- New note dialog (InputDialog) like new folder
- Bookmark star icons in file tree
- ConfirmDialog / InputDialog / Dialog system replacing native prompts
- Missing wiki-note creation dialog
- External file change watcher

Bug fixes:
- Autosave race condition (session coordinator)
- Dirty-close dialog with Save/Discard/Cancel
- Theme name mismatch in localStorage
- Context menu z-index under editor (createPortal to body)
- macOS preview pane missing glass effect
- Dialog CSS missing (Delete Note, New Folder)
- "Destination already exists" on new note (auto-increment)
- Ctrl+E preview toggle not working in editor
- Focus mode button overlapping window controls
- Graph simulation leak on close
- Trash restore/delete buttons unstyled

UI/UX:
- ARIA tree markup + keyboard navigation in sidebar
- prefers-reduced-motion support
- transition:all replaced with specific properties
- Empty states for panels
- Unified z-index/overlay rules
- Bookmark cleanup on note delete

Architecture:
- VaultIndex for global search
- Incremental backlinks via index
- Code splitting with React.lazy
- Session coordinator for tab isolation
- trash:load IPC channel
